  "texts": [
    "The features we outline draw on and speak to existing debates [e.g.5-7, 9, 29, 38, 42, 56, 58].",
    "We do not insist that these features are the only or right ones to focus on; CCC is a starting point for discussion.",
    "One might insist that Jake nevertheless makes a significant, all-ornothing difference to whether any output is made.",
    "This is true, but not important here: CCC's focus is to answer questions about who, given an output is made, makes a difference to that output, not whether an output exists in the first place.",
    "Here, we look mainly at the distribution of control between users and GenAI systems."
